import React from 'react'
import { View, Text, TextInput, StyleSheet } from 'react-native'

import HeadingText from '../components/HeadingText'
import AppTextInput from '../components/AppTextInput'
import AppButton from '../components/AppButton'

import colors from '../config/colors'
import { Fontisto } from '@expo/vector-icons'

const RegisterScreen = () => {
  return (
    <View style={styles.container}>
      <Fontisto name='blood-drop' size={100} color={colors.blood} />
      <HeadingText style={styles.heading}>Register</HeadingText>
      <View style={styles.form}>
        <AppTextInput icon='account-outline' placeholder='Name' />
        <AppTextInput icon='email' placeholder='Email' />
        <AppTextInput icon='lock' placeholder='Password' secureTextEntry />
        <AppTextInput
          icon='lock'
          placeholder='Confirm Password'
          secureTextEntry
        />
        <AppButton title='Register' />
      </View>
      <Text style={{ marginTop: 5 }}>Already have an account?</Text>
    </View>
  )
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    flex: 1,
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
  },
  heading: {
    marginVertical: 15,
  },
  form: {
    width: '100%',
    marginVertical: 5,
    paddingRight: 35,
    paddingLeft: 35,
  },
})

export default RegisterScreen
